data.description: This is it!!!  Priced over $75,000 below value for a fast sell. Great home for a growing family! This FOUR bedroom two bath home has a Newer roof (2017)  Master bedroom has a connected room that would make a nice den or office space. Both bathrooms have been updated. Home is clean and bright and ready for a new owner! Great neighborhood with no HOA! Public Utilities! Close to everything half mile walk to Southeastern University and a 5 minute drive to Florida Southern College and Lake Hollingsworth. Will Go Fast!
